{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "19.0",
      "line_index": 19,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "867512c1",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "し、失礼しますっ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "22.0",
      "line_index": 22,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d7c519aa",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──マルカっ！？　ど、どうしたんだ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.0",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "965ab577",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "入らせていただきますね……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.0",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1a7d0da3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "突然部屋のドアが開いたかと思えば、珍しく大きな声を出しているマルカ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "29.0",
      "line_index": 29,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ae6cb853",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ツカツカと俺に近づき、つり上がった目尻でじーっと見つめてくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.0",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e6e28d7b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（お、怒っているのか……？　俺マルカに何かしたっけ……？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "35.0",
      "line_index": 35,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "990bbaed",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "色々とマルカについて思い返してみるが、特に何も思い当たらない。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.0",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "37aba09c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "何て声を掛けて良いのか分からず、そのままマルカを見つめてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "39.0",
      "line_index": 39,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "64857df2",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "あ、あの……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "42.0",
      "line_index": 42,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1088eb33",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "は、はい……！　なっ、んですかっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "48.0",
      "line_index": 48,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4478e94b",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "ら、ライラ様は女王になられるお方なのです……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "48.2",
      "line_index": 48,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4478e94b",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "それはご存じですよね……！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "51.0",
      "line_index": 51,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4d44c2a4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "う、うん、知ってるけど……それがどうかしたのか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "57.0",
      "line_index": 57,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "823157b6",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "将来の女王ともあろう御方に……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "57.2",
      "line_index": 57,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "823157b6",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "その、あなたはあまりにも気安いのではないかと……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.0",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "22813dab",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そうかな……？　別に失礼になるようなことはしていないと思うけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "66.0",
      "line_index": 66,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "176eb746",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "あ、あなたがライラ様にお優しいから、その……！　うううう……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "69.0",
      "line_index": 69,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2259460f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "マルカ……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.0",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "81e8bd93",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "ライラ様がその……！　あなたと仲良くなって……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.2",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "81e8bd93",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "なりたがって……ううううううっ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "78.0",
      "line_index": 78,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6f25317f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "す、すまん……何が言いたいんだ？　もう少し分かりやすく頼む",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "82.0",
      "line_index": 82,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2956ca5c",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "わ、わたしだって……その、あなたの、こと……ううううっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "82.2",
      "line_index": 82,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2956ca5c",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "で、でも従者として、ライラ様に哀しい思いをさせるわけには……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "84.0",
      "line_index": 84,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "339d086d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "マルカは自分の考えを整理できていないのか、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "84.2",
      "line_index": 84,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "339d086d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "頭を抱え首を何度も横に振る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "85.0",
      "line_index": 85,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "433656f5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺はマルカにどう接していいのかわからず、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "85.2",
      "line_index": 85,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "433656f5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ただただマルカを見ているだけだった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "90.0",
      "line_index": 90,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3c37d980",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "あ……！　そ、そういうことだったのですね……！　理解しました……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "93.0",
      "line_index": 93,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "444b28dd",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "え……？　俺はまったく理解できていないぞ？　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "93.2",
      "line_index": 93,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "444b28dd",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "どういうことか説明してくれ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "99.0",
      "line_index": 99,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6471b58a",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "せ、性欲なんてあるから、ライラ様に気安く近づいてしまうんですねっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "102.0",
      "line_index": 102,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "710297ec",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──は……？　す、すまん、本当に話が見えなくて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "102.2",
      "line_index": 102,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "710297ec",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "なんでそういうことになるんだよ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "108.0",
      "line_index": 108,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "99f4b8c6",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "ら、ライラ様を毒牙から守護らねば……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "108.2",
      "line_index": 108,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "99f4b8c6",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "それがライラ様の従者としてのわたしの役目です……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "111.0",
      "line_index": 111,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "eed6ca42",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うわっ！　マルカ！　ちょ……！　ず、ズボン脱がして何するつもりだ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "117.0",
      "line_index": 117,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2cb9bc76",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "初めからこうすればすべて解決できたんですね……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "117.2",
      "line_index": 117,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2cb9bc76",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "ライラ様への忠誠も、あなたへの想いも同時に解決できます……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.0",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8652cfc2",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "さぁ大人しくしていてください……！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.2",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8652cfc2",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "だ、だいじょうぶ……心得は一応ありますから……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "137.0",
      "line_index": 137,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "53afbb97",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "ぢゅるっ♥　ちゅっ♥　ぢゅるるっ♥　れるぅ……ぢゅる……れるれるぅ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "140.0",
      "line_index": 140,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "853d237e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "う、うう……マルカ……！　や、やめろって……！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "140.2",
      "line_index": 140,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "853d237e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "なんでいきなり……くっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "143.0",
      "line_index": 143,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6aef6359",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "怒った表情で肉棒を咥えると、いきなりフェラをしてくるマルカ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "144.0",
      "line_index": 144,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b80e113a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "マルカの鬼気迫る表情にただただ戸惑い、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "144.2",
      "line_index": 144,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b80e113a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "されるがままに肉棒を刺激されていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "147.0",
      "line_index": 147,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "aa4cb0e8",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "う、うう……♥　本で見たのより全然大きい……♥ ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "147.2",
      "line_index": 147,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "aa4cb0e8",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "でもできないわけじゃない……♥　このまま続けていれば……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "147.4",
      "line_index": 147,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "aa4cb0e8",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "ぢゅるるるっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "150.0",
      "line_index": 150,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "42784fc5",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ふっ！　く……！　待てって……落ち着けマルカ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "150.2",
      "line_index": 150,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "42784fc5",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そ、そんな慌てなくても……くううっ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "153.0",
      "line_index": 153,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8edf64ee",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "口を窄め肉棒を吸い上げるマルカ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.0",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2f540d4e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "真面目なマルカがフェラをする……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.2",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2f540d4e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それが異様なまでの背徳感を呼び、さらに肉棒を怒張させてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "157.0",
      "line_index": 157,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ba3d0a9f",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "さ、先っぽから……しょっぱくて……エッチな液を出して……♥ ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "157.2",
      "line_index": 157,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ba3d0a9f",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "やはり性欲が……毒気をすぐに抜かないと……♥　れるぅ♥　ちゅ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "159.0",
      "line_index": 159,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5f5da9ce",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だんだんと頬が紅く染まり、表情がいやらしくなっていくマルカ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "160.0",
      "line_index": 160,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d8120a15",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ゾクゾクした刺激が何度も背筋を駆け上り、腰がビクンと跳ねてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "163.0",
      "line_index": 163,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "33393f84",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "ど、どんどんエッチな液……出て……♥　マルカで",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "163.2",
      "line_index": 163,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "33393f84",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "おちんちん喜んでる……♥　あなたが気持ち良くなっている……♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "163.4",
      "line_index": 163,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "33393f84",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "う、嬉しい……♥　もっと感じて……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.0",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d7da2ee3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "最初の勢いに任せたフェラから、献身的なフェラに動きが変わっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "167.0",
      "line_index": 167,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2f230966",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "優しく肉棒を吸い上げ、裏筋を舌先でくにくにと舐める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "168.0",
      "line_index": 168,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3d4870ac",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "マルカを止めなければ、そんな気持ちは思考から完全に消え、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "168.2",
      "line_index": 168,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3d4870ac",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "マルカに身も心も預けるように、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "168.4",
      "line_index": 168,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "3d4870ac",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "心地良く気持ち良いフェラに身を委ねてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "171.0",
      "line_index": 171,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ac272323",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "そ、その顔……どきどきしてきます……♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "171.2",
      "line_index": 171,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ac272323",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "もっと、もっと感じて……♥ 今だけマルカのこと考えて……♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "171.4",
      "line_index": 171,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "ac272323",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "あなたの心の中マルカでいっぱいにして……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "173.0",
      "line_index": 173,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "37923d8a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "反り返った肉棒をぢゅるぢゅると吸い上げ続けるマルカ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "174.0",
      "line_index": 174,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bba8e1f4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その気持ち良さに射精感が強くなり、堪えきれなくなっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "178.0",
      "line_index": 178,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "36a199c8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "マルカ……！　も、もう……！　離れてくれ……このままじゃっ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "182.0",
      "line_index": 182,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "744e038d",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "嫌……このまま……出して……♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "182.2",
      "line_index": 182,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "744e038d",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "ぢゅるるっ！♥　れるぅっ！♥　んぅ！♥ ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "182.4",
      "line_index": 182,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "744e038d",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "ちゅっ♥　ちゅぅ……ぢゅぞぞぞっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "185.0",
      "line_index": 185,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3747d04b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あっ！　あっ！　も、もうダメ……これ以上我慢できない……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "185.2",
      "line_index": 185,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3747d04b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うう、で、出るっ！！　く、う、ううううっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "196.0",
      "line_index": 196,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e466649e",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "んふぅっ！？♥　ん……んぅぅぅ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "196.2",
      "line_index": 196,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e466649e",
      "speaker": "マルカ",
      "ja": "ごく……ごくっ♥　んぅぅ……ふぅ……んんんっ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
